Class JAXBProductDESMarshaller

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sourceforge.waters.model.marshaller.JAXBMarshaller<ProductDESProxy,ProductDES>
      • net.sourceforge.waters.model.marshaller.JAXBProductDESMarshaller
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProxyMarshaller<ProductDESProxy>, ProxyUnmarshaller<ProductDESProxy>

    public class JAXBProductDESMarshaller
extends JAXBMarshaller<ProductDESProxy,ProductDES>

    A helper class to read and write Waters Product DES (.wdes) files.

    The most convenient way to use a JAXBProductDESMarshaller is to create an instance and register it with a DocumentManager as a marshaller and/or unmarshaller. The DocumentManager can automatically recognise files by their extension and use the appropriate marshaller to load or save their contents.

    Author:
    Robi Malik
    See Also:
    DocumentManager
